 <paragraph index="47" node_type="writer" parent_index="12">Auto generate ID number/string for each new entry </paragraph>
 <paragraph index="48" node_type="writer" parent_index="12">* Create option to merge entries in case duplicate entries are captured</paragraph>
 <paragraph index="49" node_type="writer" parent_index="12">* Note that where the same story appears in a separate edition (e.g. am or pm) or is reprinted in another title, or online, these should reflect as distinct entries. </paragraph>
 <paragraph index="55" node_type="writer" parent_index="12">News Report ID (source)</paragraph>
 <paragraph index="58" node_type="writer" parent_index="12">The file name (where relevant) of a PDF or similar object as generated by the report source such as a news archive service. </paragraph>
 <paragraph index="67" node_type="writer" parent_index="12">News Report URL</paragraph>
 <paragraph index="70" node_type="writer" parent_index="12">Where relevant (i.e. online news page); URLs tend to age out, so an archive must be saved to show the site/page as it was at the time of input. </paragraph>
 <paragraph index="73" node_type="writer" parent_index="12">Must generate an entry on the Wayback machine or similar online archiving service. </paragraph>
